high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room towards the piano, then take a right and face the desk to the right of the piano.
Pick up the remote on the right side of the desk.
Turn around and walk across the room then turn around to the right and face the side of the arm chair.
Place the remote in the arm chair.
Walk forward to the arm chair, then turn right and walk forward to face the shelves in the wall.
Pick up the remote on the top shelf.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left of the armchair and turn right to face the armchair.
Place the remote on the arm chair next to the other remote.
anns.task_desc: To gather two remotes and place them on the arm chair.

high_descs: Turn around and go around the couch behind you and keeping it to the right until you reach a small, black desk
Pick up the remote from the small black table
Turn around and go towards the Television before turning to the right in front of the television and turning right again to face the chair
Place the remote behind the pillow on the chair
Turn right and move past the couch to the left towards the shelves
Pick up the remote from the shelf
Turn around and go back between the television and the foot stool before turning right to face the chair
place the second remote behind the first remote on the chair
anns.task_desc: Placing two remote controls on a chair

high_descs: Go around the furniture to the small black table on the right side of the piano.
Pick up the remote on the table.
Turn around and go to the right side of the chair in front of the TV.
Place the remote on the chair's seat next to the cushion.
Go around the furniture towards to bookshelf across the living room.
Pick up the remote on the bookshelf.
Turn around and go back to right side of the chair in front of the TV.
Place the remote on the seat of the chair behind the cushion and the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Put the remotes on the same chair.
